subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Radwanska, the first player to reach the final four at the Australian Open, will face Serena Williams. In the men’s draw, Milos Raonic used a serve-and-volley game plan to beat Stan Wawrinka.
